    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking into some expansion plans for my cafe in a small town where the cost of living is pretty low. i've been hearing a lot of talk about the new minimum wage proposals in the state. how do these kinds of wage hikes usually impact small businesses in places like mine?",
