    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see what u mean about the costs. but i also hear people saying that if workers have more money they'll spend more at local shops, which helps everyone. is that actually a real thing that happens, or is it just a theory people use to justify the hikes?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
